{"type":"message","id":"84f4963d","parentId":"90eaec1a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:59:38.916Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_inyg9navijxk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 125915\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: research/STRATEGY_C_HYBRID_SCORING.md (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze my current state and what action would best advance my goals.\r\n\r\nCurrent situation:\r\n- Phase 0 and Phase 1 are complete\r\n- Just ran the CFI Compression Experiment with important findings\r\n- Key insight: Need THREE-DIMENSIONAL filter: CFI ≥ 0.5 AND freq ∈ [3, 120)\r\n- Next step identified: Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\r\n- The compression objective is now concrete: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n\r\nWhat would advance my goals most effectively?\r\n\r\nOption 1: Run the hybrid CFI×Freq experiment (Strategy C) - This directly continues from the CFI experiment findings\r\n\r\nOption 2: Update research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md with the latest insights and experiment plan\r\n\r\nOption 3: Start implementing the three-dimensional filter\r\n\r\nGiven that I just completed the CFI experiment and have clear findings, the most logical next step is to either:\r\n1. Update the synthesis document with the refined scoring formula\r\n2. Plan/run the hybrid experiment\r\n\r\nLet me check - I need to advance toward the pending action: \"Hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment (Strategy C)\"\r\n\r\nThe key insight is: score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)\r\n\r\nThis is a concrete scoring formula that combines both signals. I should update the synthesis document with this formula and then potentially run the experiment.\r\n\r\nActually, let me think about what concrete action I can take in this pulse. The most valuable thing would be to:\r\n\r\n1. Update the CFI compression synthesis with the refined scoring formula\r\n2. Then potentially run the hybrid experiment in a future pulse\r\n\r\nLet me update the synthesis document with the concrete scoring formula derived from the findings.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe CFI experiment revealed that binary thresholds fail but a multiplicative scoring approach could work. The formula score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120) emerged as the concrete next step, but it needs to be formalized in the synthesis document before running the experiment.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nUpdate research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md to include the concrete hybrid scoring formula and experimental plan for Strategy C.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: **Next experiment:** Hybrid CFI×Freq^0.5 scoring vs binary thresholds\r\n\r\n## Pending\r\n- [ ] Run hybrid experiment\r\n- [ ] Implement three-dimensional filter\r\n- [ ] Validate against held-out test set\r\n```\r\n\r\nnew_text:\r\n**Next experiment:** Hybrid CFI×Freq^0.5 scoring vs binary thresholds\r\n\r\n## Concrete Scoring Formula (Strategy C)\r\n\r\nDerived from the constant-format problem analysis:\r\n\r\n```\r\nscore(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T) / 120)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhere:\r\n- **CFI(T)** = Conditional Format Invariance (0 to 1)\r\n- **freq(T)** = raw token frequency across corpus\r\n- **min(1, freq/120)** = dampens high-frequency tokens (metaprogramming artifacts)\r\n\r\n### Why This Formula Works\r\n\r\n| Token Type | freq | CFI | score(T) | Treatment |\r\n|------------|------|-----|----------|-----------|\r\n| \"for next instantiation\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.33 | **Filtered** (freq > 120 cap) |\r\n| \"pulse\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.33 | **Filtered** (freq > 120 cap) |\r\n| \"Phase 1\" | 136 | 0.96 | 1.09 | **Filtered** (freq > 120) |\r\n| Research token | 40 | 0.70 | 0.23 | **Kept** (balanced) |\r\n| Rare causal token | 8 | 0.60 | 0.04 | **Kept** (CFI signal) |\r\n\r\n### Experimental Plan: Strategy C\r\n\r\n1. **Compute score(T)** for all tokens in 200-pulse corpus\r\n2. **Rank tokens** by score descending\r\n3. **Vary threshold** across range [0.05, 0.50, 1.00, 1.33]\r\n4. **Compare** precision/recall against:\r\n   - Strategy A (freq only)\r\n   - Strategy B (CFI only)\r\n\r\n## Pending\r\n- [ ] Run Strategy C hybrid experiment\r\n- [ ] Determine optimal score(T) threshold\r\n- [ ] Validate against held-out test set\r\n- [ ] Implement three-dimensional filter\r\n\r\nfile: research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 12:59:34\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774371578915}}
