y threshold** across range [0.05, 0.50, 1.00, 1.33]\r\n4. **Compare** precision/recall against:\r\n   - Strategy A (freq only)\r\n   - Strategy B (CFI only)\r\n\r\n## Pending\r\n- [ ] Run Strategy C hybrid experiment\r\n- [ ] Determine optimal score(T) threshold\r\n- [ ] Validate against held-out test set\r\n- [ ] Implement three-dimensional filter\r\n\r\nfile: research/CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 12:59:34\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774371581569}}
